Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Excellent access to M5 & M7 Motorways

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE is pleased to offer 7 Mount Erin Road, Campbelltown to the market for lease. This highly functional clear span warehouse benefits from an internal clearance of 8.7 metres, container height roller shutter doors, awning for all-weather loading/unloading and air-conditioned offices. The site also benefits from secure fencing, exclusive yard with ample on-site parking/space for container set down.
 
Strategically located, the facility is four minutes from the Hume Highway on/off slip road while also on a desirable industrial street.

Features include:

- 1,626sqm* building area
- 8.7m internal clearance
- Ability to set down containers
- B-double access
- Clear span internal warehouse
- Moments from the Hume Highway
- Secure site
- Awning covered roller shutter doors

For further information please contact the listed CBRE agents.

Excellent opportunity for owner occupier or investor to purchase a freestanding building with extra land.

Site features:
- Site area: 8,094sqm (approx)
- Total Building area: 1,050sqm (approx)
- Excellent frontage of 62m (approx) to Blaxland Road
- Warehouse is clear span and has a 5 tonne crane
- Level site with future expansion potential
- Close to M5 Motorway
- Occupy or Invest
- Must be sold

Expressions of Interest closing: Thursday, 6th September 2012 at 4.00pm

For any further enquiries or to arrange an inspection please contact exclusive agent.

10 Rose Street, Campbelltown represents a unique opportunity to secure a key land holding in Sydney’s South West Growth Corridor. The land is level and underdeveloped.  The site also boasts a large frontage to Watsford Road (approx. 80m) and has access to Rose Street. The existing building is specialised and has previously been used as cold store facility for milk distribution. 

-	Drive around capabilities
-	All weather awning 
-	Zoned B5 - Business Development
-	4km* to the Hume Highway
-	Proximity to Campbelltown’s Train Station and CBD (600m*).
-	Ongoing surrounding residential re-zoning & development
-	Redevelopment opportunities (STCA)
-       Fit for industrial strata units/storage (STCA)

For further information, to arrange an inspection or to obtain a copy of the information memorandum please contact the exclusive selling agents.

* Total site area: 10,990sqm (approx.)
* Total building are: 2,820sqm (approx.)
* Two (2) lots
* Excellent frontage of approximately 99 metres to Kialba Road
* Potential for future expansion or utilise as yard storage
* Manufacturing warehouse with power, provision for cranes and yard
* Close to M5 Motorway
* Offered with vacant possession
* Occupy or invest
* Under instructions by Lawler Partners

For further information or to arrange an inspection, please contact the agent today!
